version":"white","text":"They go wherever the wind takes them. On rainy days, their bodies are heavier, so they take shelter beneath big trees."},{"version":"black-2","text":"Perhaps because they feel more at ease in a group, they stick to others they find. They end up looking like a cloud."},{"version":"white-2","text":"Perhaps because they feel more at ease in a group, they stick to others they find. They end up looking like a cloud."},{"version":"x","text":"When attacked, it escapes by shooting cotton from its body. The cotton serves as a decoy to distract the attacker."},{"version":"y","text":"Perhaps because they feel more at ease in a group, they stick to others they find. They end up looking like a cloud."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"When attacked, it escapes by shooting cotton from its body. The cotton serves as a decoy to distract the attacker."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Perhaps because they feel more at ease in a group, they stick to others they find. They end up looking like a cloud."},{"version":"sun","text":"When it finds others of its kind, they all stick together. When enough of them have collected, the mass resembles a cumulonimbus cloud."},{"version":"moon","text":"Pillows and beds stuffed with cotton exhaled by Cottonee are soft and puffy, light and airy\u2014 altogether top quality."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"To protect itself, it shoots cotton from its body. When it gets wet in the rain, its cotton grows moist and heavy, and it can\u2019t move as well."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"When attacked, it expels cotton from its body to create a diversion. The cotton it loses grows back in quickly."},{"version":"sword","text":"It shoots cotton from its body to protect itself. If it gets caught up in hurricane-strength winds, it can get sent to the other side of the Earth."},{"version":"shield","text":"Weaving together the cotton of both Cottonee and Eldegoss produces exquisite cloth that\u2019s highly prized by many luxury brands."}],"evo":{"name":"cottonee","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"whimsicott","level":1,"min_level":null,"trigger":"use-item","item":"sun-stone","held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]}]},"sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/546.png","shiny":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/shiny/546.png","capture":190,"happiness":70,"growth":"medium","gender":4,"hatch":20,"ev":{"speed":1},"forms":[]}